{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "iknos-be-collection-001",
    "name": "IKNOS-BE API",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap untuk menguji seluruh endpoint API iknos-be.\n\n**Alur pengujian yang direkomendasikan (jalankan secara berurutan):**\n\n1. 🔐 Auth — Register & Login (User 1 & User 2)\n2. 👤 Users — Profile & Avatar\n3. 🏠 Rooms — Buat Room, Lihat, Detail\n4. 🚪 Rooms — Join & Approval\n5. 📝 Notes — Buat, Lihat, Hapus Note\n6. 🚶 Rooms — Leave Room\n\n> Token JWT & room_id diisi **otomatis** oleh Test Scripts masing-masing request.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🏥 Health Check",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Cek apakah server berjalan dengan baik."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Server running', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('ok');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User 1 (Owner)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{user1_username}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{user1_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user1_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Daftarkan User 1 sebagai Owner Room. Token JWT disimpan otomatis ke `token_user1`."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Registrasi berhasil', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token');",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token_user1', json.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('[User1] Token disimpan:', json.data.token.substring(0,30) + '...');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
